### Update OwnerShip
PATCH {{host}}/api/v1/restaurants/{{restaurantId}}/transfer-ownership
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: {{adminId}}

{
  "newOwnerId": "c835a1e5-dd1c-4404-a632-91604a9d4505"
